 lead gen and waitlist campaigns<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3228\" data-end=\"3272\">\n<p data-start=\"3230\" data-end=\"3272\">Position the founders as thought leaders<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3274\" data-end=\"3352\">We handle execution so your internal team can focus on product and operations.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1716044875498{background-color: #ffffff !important;}&#8221;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3359\" data-end=\"3407\"><strong data-start=\"3363\" data-end=\"3407\">6. Brands With Limited Internal Capacity<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3409\" data-end=\"3596\">If you\u2019re too busy running your business to manage your social pages\u2014or you\u2019ve tried hiring internally without consistent results\u2014then outsourcing to an expert agency delivers better ROI.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3598\" data-end=\"3686\">We become your external team\u2014strategy, design, copy, engagement, analytics\u2014all included.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3598\" data-end=\"3686\">If any of these profiles describe your organisation, then it\u2019s time to invest in structured, strategic, and professionally managed social media. And Aminifu Digital Agency is here to help you do it right.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1716309664788{padding-top: 150px !important;padding-bottom: 150px !important;background: #ffffff url(https:\/\/aminifudigital.co.ke\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/what-is-social-media-marketing.jpg?id=2953) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-star